1. install
a. 安装好anaconda3
b. conda create -n tensorflow python=3.5
c. activate
activate tensorflow
pip install --upgrade --ignore-installed tensorflow (cpu版本）
或
pip install tensorflow-gpu （gpu版本， 要求cude8环境）
d. deactivate
e. 测试
import tensorflow as tf
print(tf.__version__)


异常处理:
如果在windows下面import tensorflow报错, 需要指定这样的路径:
D:\Program Files\Anaconda3\envs\tensorflow>python.exe
Python 3.5.4 |Continuum Analytics, Inc.| (default, Aug 14 2017, 13:41:13) [MSC v
.1900 64 bit (AMD64)] on win32
Type "help", "copyright", "credits" or "license" for more information.
>>> import tensorflow
>>> exit()

D:\Program Files\Anaconda3\envs\tensorflow>
